<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ka">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>კონფერენციის განრიგი</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Segoe+UI:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #764ba2;
            background-color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon">📋</div>
        <h1>კონფერენციის პროგრამა</h1>
        <p>მოგესალმებით! აქ შეგიძლიათ იხილოთ მომხსენებელთა განრიგი და პრეზენტაციების ბმულები.</p>
        
        <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1skNNfof9BrIdvbB6MJ60rda8DgDPfpGjfjFdz_GJhgc/edit?usp=sharing" 
           target="_blank" 
           class="btn">
           განრიგის ნახვა
        </a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
